aboutSection.title: Frontend Developer!
aboutSection.describe:
Hello, I am Duong Khang Hy, an accountable and creative individual, always seeking opportunities for growth and learning. My strengths lie in effective teamwork, good communication skills, and flexible problem-solving abilities. However, my weaknesses include the need to improve time management skills and maintaining mental stability in high-pressure environments.

I aspire to work at this company because I believe it offers a creative, exciting work environment and vast career development opportunities. I want to contribute to the company's mission and growth goals through my experience and capabilities, while learning and developing myself to reach the highest potential in my career.
